<lb n="0388b08" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><note n="0388001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】大日本續藏經</note><jhead>佛頂尊勝陀羅尼注義</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0388b09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0388b10" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智
<lb n="0388b11" ed="T"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0388b12" ed="T"/><div1 type="dharani"><p id="pT19p0388b1201" type="dharani">曩謨婆<note place="inline">上</note>&CB00344;&CB00085;帝<note place="inline">歸命世尊</note>怛&CB00770;<note place="inline">二合</note>路枳也<note place="inline">三世亦三界</note>
<lb n="0388b13" ed="T"/>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底尾始瑟吒<note place="inline">二合</note>野<note place="inline">最殊勝</note>沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>也<note place="inline">大覺者</note>
<lb n="0388b14" ed="T"/>婆&CB00344;&CB00085;帝<note place="inline">同前</note>怛&CB00135;也他<note place="inline">引。所謂。亦即說</note>唵<note place="inline">亦云一切法本不生。
<lb n="0388b15" ed="T"/>亦云三藏。亦云如來無見頂相也</note>尾戍馱也<note place="inline">淨除</note>尾戍馱也娑摩娑
<lb n="0388b16" ed="T"/>摩三滿多<note place="inline">上</note>&CB00085;婆娑<note place="inline">普遍照曜</note>娑頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉拏<note place="inline">舒遍</note>&CB03442;
<lb n="0388b17" ed="T"/>底&CB00344;訶曩<note place="inline">六趣稠林</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;尾舜<note place="inline">入</note>弟<note place="inline">自性清淨</note>阿
<lb n="0388b18" ed="T"/>毘詵者&CB00418;&CB00805;<note place="inline">灌頂我</note>素&CB03442;多<note place="inline">善逝</note>&CB00085;囉&CB00085;者曩<note place="inline">引。殊勝言
<lb n="0388b19" ed="T"/>教</note>阿蜜哩<note place="inline">二合</note>多<note place="inline">去</note>毘灑罽<note place="inline">甘露灌頂。亦云不死句灌頂。露者法身解脫</note>
<lb n="0388b20" ed="T"/>阿<note place="inline">引</note>訶囉阿訶囉<note place="inline">云唯願攝受。唯垂授攝受。亦云遍攘脫諸苦惱</note>阿欲散
<lb n="0388b21" ed="T"/>馱<note place="inline">引</note>囉抳<note place="inline">任持受命</note>戍馱也戍馱也<note place="inline">清淨修修</note>&CB00344;&CB00344;曩尾戍
<lb n="0388b22" ed="T"/>第<note place="inline">如虛空清淨</note>鄔瑟膩<note place="inline">二合</note>沙尾惹也尾舜<note place="inline">入</note>第<note place="inline">佛頂最清
<lb n="0388b23" ed="T"/>淨</note>娑訶娑囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉濕弭<note place="inline">二合<note n="0388002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">十＝千？</note><sic cert="?" n="0388002" resp="Taisho" corr="千">十</sic>光明</note>散祖&CB00135;帝<note place="inline">驚覺</note>
<lb n="0388b24" ed="T"/>薩&CB00085;怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB03442;多地瑟吒<note place="inline">二合引</note>曩<note place="inline">引</note>地瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0388b25" ed="T"/>多<note place="inline">一切如來神力所加持</note>摩訶母捺哩<note place="inline">二合。印契。若廣釋。身印語印心印。金剛印。如理
<lb n="0388b26" ed="T"/>趣般若說</note>&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>迦也僧訶多<note place="inline">上</note>曩尾舜第<note place="inline">金剛鉤鎖
<lb n="0388b27" ed="T"/>身清淨</note>薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;囉拏播野訥&CB03442;底跛哩尾舜弟
<lb n="0388b28" ed="T"/><note place="inline">一<note n="0388003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">切＋（障）？</note><sic cert="?" n="0388003" resp="Taisho" corr="切障">切</sic>清淨。一切障者。所謂業障報障煩惱障。皆得清淨也</note>&CB00425;羅<note place="inline">二合</note>底&CB00135;靺多
<lb n="0388b29" ed="T"/>也阿欲舜<note place="inline">入</note>第<note place="inline">壽命增長皆得清淨</note>三麼耶地瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>帝
<pb n="0388c" id="T19.0974D.0388c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0388c01" ed="T"/><note place="inline">誓願加持</note>麼抳麼抳摩訶麼抳<note place="inline">世寶法寶。所謂福德智慧<note n="0388004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二？</note><sic cert="?" n="0388004" resp="Taisho" corr="二">三</sic>種資糧</note>怛他
<lb n="0388c02" ed="T"/>多步多句致跛哩舜<note place="inline">入</note>第<note place="inline">真如實際遍滿清淨</note>尾薩普<note place="inline"><note n="0388005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">六＝二&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0388005" resp="【原】" corr="二">六</sic>合</note>
<lb n="0388c03" ed="T"/>吒沒地舜<note place="inline">入</note>第<note place="inline">顯現智慧清淨</note>惹也惹也<note place="inline">最勝最勝。真俗二諦</note>尾惹
<lb n="0388c04" ed="T"/>也尾惹也<note place="inline"><note n="0388006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">昧勝勝＝殊勝殊勝&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0388006" resp="【原】" corr="殊勝殊勝">昧勝勝</sic>悲智二門</note>娑麼<note place="inline">二合</note>囉娑麼<note place="inline">二合</note>囉<note place="inline">念<note n="0388007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">待＝持？</note><sic cert="?" n="0388007" resp="Taisho" corr="持">待</sic>
<lb n="0388c05" ed="T"/>定慧<note n="0388008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">相＋（應）？</note><sic cert="?" n="0388008" resp="Taisho" corr="相應">相</sic></note>薩&CB00085;沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>地瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>多舜第<note place="inline">入而佛加持清淨</note>&CB00085;
<lb n="0388c06" ed="T"/>曰&CB00942;<note place="inline">二合菩提心堅固如金剛也</note>&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB03442;陛<note place="inline">證金剛藏</note>&CB00085;曰覽
<lb n="0388c07" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">願成金剛</note>&CB00418;麼麼<note place="inline"><note n="0388009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">或＝我？</note><sic cert="?" n="0388009" resp="Taisho" corr="我">或</sic>議或為他念誦稱彼名字</note>設哩嚂薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0388c08" ed="T"/>薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>難<note place="inline">引</note>者迦也尾舜弟<note place="inline">一切有情身清<note n="0388010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">清＝淨？</note><sic cert="?" n="0388010" resp="Taisho" corr="淨">清</sic></note>薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0388c09" ed="T"/>&CB03442;底跛哩舜第<note place="inline">一切趣皆清淨</note>薩&CB00085;怛他&CB03442;多三麼濕
<lb n="0388c10" ed="T"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>娑地瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">一切如來安慰<note n="0388011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">命＝令？</note><sic cert="?" n="0388011" resp="Taisho" corr="令">命</sic>得加持</note>沒&CB00833;<note place="inline">二合</note>沒
<lb n="0388c11" ed="T"/>&CB00833;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00155;馱也<note place="inline">令悟能覺。令悟能覺</note>舜第<note place="inline">普遍清淨</note>薩&CB00085;怛他
<lb n="0388c12" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>&CB03442;多<note place="inline">引</note>地瑟<note place="inline">二合馱</note>曩地瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>多<note place="inline">一切如來神力所加持</note>
<lb n="0388c13" ed="T"/>摩訶母怛&CB03272;<note place="inline">二合大印。所謂大印由入毘盧遮那曼荼羅。受灌頂已後。灌頂師受得本尊瑜伽三
<lb n="0388c14" ed="T"/>麼地。觀智一念淨心。瑜伽相應行者別尊心等同毘盧遮那及諸菩薩。能現入相成道。速證薩婆若智也</note></p><p id="pT19p0388c1441" place="inline">娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0388c15" ed="T"/>訶者涅槃義。所謂四涅槃。一自性清淨涅槃。
<lb n="0388c16" ed="T"/>二有餘依涅槃。三無餘依涅槃。四無住處涅
<lb n="0388c17" ed="T"/>槃。如上所譯。唐梵敵對。顯句標釋。</p></div1>
<lb n="0388c18" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0388c19" ed="T"/><div1 type="W"><p id="pT19p0388c1901">寶永二年<note place="inline">乙酉</note>冬十二月十三日以如來藏
<lb n="0388c20" ed="T"/>本書寫竟　　兜率谷雞頭院闍梨嚴覺</p>
<lb n="0388c21" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0388c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0388c2201">享保三歲戊戌九月令得忍寫校正了</p>
<lb n="0388c23" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0388c2301">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　慈泉</p>
<lb n="0388c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0388c2401">文政六年癸未六月以東叡山真如院本令
<lb n="0388c25" ed="T"/>他寫自校之了　　　　　　　　龍肝</p></div1>
